casebody.data:
Milorad Teodor OLIC, petitioner,
v.
M. Eliot SPEARMAN, Warden. No. 18-5873. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 5, 2018.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States *461Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
